<H3>Total   	1,988 </H3>

1. Source: Republican National Committee, Chief Counsel's Office,
as of November 27, 1995.  Not shown are the Democratic schedule
and delegate numbers.  The Democratic nominating process is expected
to be a mere formality. 
<P>
<P>
