<HEAD>

<TITLE>Town Hall Spotlight: The Right to Life - Jan 1996</TITLE>

</HEAD>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/paper2.jpg">  
<P>

<CENTER>
<img src="/townhall/spotlights/1-22-96/rtlspot.gif">
<br><H2>The Right to Life & The March for Life 1996</CENTER></H2>
<center>
<img src="/townhall/spotlights/1-22-96/image12.gif">
<br><a href="/townhall/spotlights/1-22-96/photos.html">Other photos from the March</a></center>
<br>
Monday, January 22nd marks the twenty-third year since the Roe v. Wade Supreme Court decison in 1973.  On Monday, thousand of people will participate in the March for Life and Town Hall will be there to capture it.  This week Town Hall will bring you the best pro-life information available to you on the net.  Also we will bring you the latest information that various Town Hall citizens have available for you.
<P>
<P>
<P>
<P>
<HR>
<P><a name="week"></a>

<CENTER><h2><a name="Misc">The Right to LIfe</a></h2> <br>

</center><p>

