<html>

<head>
<title>Columnist Dr. Edwin J. Feulner, Jr.</title>
</head>


<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<center>

<img src="/townhall/columnists/colm.gif">






</center>





<h5><a href="/townhall/columnists/i-feulner.html.cgi/textonly">[Text View]</a></h5>

<center>
<h2>Dr. Edwin J. Feulner, Jr.</h2>
</center>


<p>


<img align="left" alt="Photo of Dr. Edwin J. Feulner, Jr." 
hspace=8 vspace=25 src="/heritage/staff/pics/feulner.gif">


