http://www.conservative.org:80/townhall/sotu96/sotu.html 204.71.237.88 19970208192550 text/html 41486
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 19:26:28 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 24-Jan-96 14:00:26 GMT
Content-length: 41297
